title: The Apartment you've been dreaming of, Just came available!
posting_body: ['8200 Bridgeport Way Southwest, Lakewood, WA 98499', 'Timbre Apartments in Lakewood, WASurrounded by beautiful trees and greenery, Timbre Apartments offers one, two, and three-bedroom floor plans conveniently located in Lakewood.', 'Residents enjoy spending time in the clubhouse working remotely, playing shuffleboard and foosball, and outdoor swimming in the pool, playing cornhole and sitting by the fire pits.', 'Our community is conveniently located in Lakewood, near restaurants, grocery stores, and schools such as Dower Elementary, Lochburn Middle, and Clover Park High School.', 'Schedule your tour today to see why so many people love calling Timbre Apartments home.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Garbage Disposal', 'Washer/Dryer', 'Fireplaces in select homes', 'Dishwasher', 'Private Patio/Balcony', 'Oversized Closets', 'Community Features:', 'Dishwasher', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Spacious Floorplans', 'Cable Ready', 'Fitness Center', 'Pet Friendly', 'Swimming Pool', 'Playground', 'Bocce Ball Lawn', 'Fire Pit', 'Jogging Trail', 'On-Site Maintenance', 'On-Site Management', 'Online Service Requests', 'Resident Lounge', 'Interactive Walking Trail', 'Outdoor Lounge & Fire Pits', 'Translation Service Available', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
